{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"9":"The Chapters on Marriage"},"section_detail":{"9":{"hadithnumber_first":1845,"hadithnumber_last":2015,"arabicnumber_first":1845,"arabicnumber_last":2015}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1941,"arabicnumber":1941,"text":"। ‘আয়িশাহ্ (রাঃ) থেকে বর্ণিত। নবী সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়াসাল্লাম বলেনঃ এক ঢোক বা দু’ ঢোক দুধপানে (দুধপান জনিত) বৈবাহিক নিষিদ্ধতা প্রতিষ্ঠিত হয় না।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":9,"hadith":97}}]}